							                           		<h2>More Information</h2>
														                           <p><strong>Under contract by MTRWestern</strong>&nbsp;<br>Customer Contact:&nbsp;<br>971-358-0623</p><p><strong>Managed by Clackamas County Social Services</strong>&nbsp;<br>Please contact us directly to request a schedule in an alternate format, or with any complaints or concerns:&nbsp;<br>PO Box 2950, Oregon City, OR 97045&nbsp;<br>503-655-8640, TTY 503-650-5646</p><p><strong>The Clackamas County Connects Shuttle Service Respects Civil Rights</strong></p><ul><li><a href="https://dochub.clackamas.us/documents/drupal/8a7f8cfb-9407-4ecf-bf03-345a2c6a3f25">CCSD ADA Plan</a></li><li><a href="https://dochub.clackamas.us/documents/drupal/6d0e8603-c253-4352-8d4e-5932c0faed0f">Reasonable Modification Policy</a></li><li><a href="https://dochub.clackamas.us/documents/drupal/bb357609-bdad-4b16-958a-18b1fd9b1301">Clackamas County ADA Complaint Form</a></li><li><a href="https://dochub.clackamas.us/documents/drupal/406455d1-a3e9-4357-bc89-cb0bc0e8eb8c">CCSSD Title VI Plan</a></li></ul>
							
